        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 17. Metathorax of species of Anchylorhynchus, ventral view. Scales: 500 µm. A A. trapezicollis. B A. aegrotus C A. vanini, male. D A. vanini, female." ;
